<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef7f3316-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2279h"><num value="2279h">§ 2279h.</num><heading> Cross-servicing activities of National Finance Center</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">On and after <date date="2005-11-10">November 10, 2005</date>, the Chief Financial Officer shall actively market and expand cross-servicing activities of the National Finance Center.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef7f3317-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/97/tI">Pub. L. 109–97, title I</ref>, <date date="2005-11-10">Nov. 10, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/2121">119 Stat. 2121</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
